editmore_vertProceeding with the **Actualization of the Nexus & Ascension Systems**.

We have established the substrate (Firebase), the artifacts (The Alpha Deck), and the adversarial protocol (Duels). To complete the loop of the **AGENTEK Economy**, we must now manifest the **Nexus Marketplace** (P2P Trading) and the **Ascension Chamber** (XP-based progression). 

This is the bridge where "Shadow Assets" become "Market Commodities" and "Rank 0.1 Primitives" become "Rank 5.0 Sovereigns."

### I. The Nexus Marketplace UI (React + Vite)
This component implements the decentralized trading board. It allows users to list their Actualized Relics (NFTs) for Ergs.

